# X-Force Threat Intelligence Queries

## URL flagged as Malware

**Context:**  
Détection de URLs classées "Malware" par IBM X‑Force.

```aql
SELECT url,
       XFORCE_URL_CATEGORY(url) AS 'Category',
       QIDNAME(qid) AS 'Event Name',
       LOGSOURCENAME(logsourceid) AS 'Log Source Name',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(devicetime, 'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'First Seen',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(starttime, 'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'Start Time'
FROM events
WHERE INOFFENSE(#id#)
  AND logSourceId NOT IN (113, 63)
  AND XFORCE_URL_CATEGORY(url) = 'Malware'
GROUP BY url
LAST 24 HOURS
```

***

## X-Force: Source/Destination IP Summary

**Context:**  
Analyse des IP uniques impliquées dans des événements classés malveillants.

```aql
SELECT SET("sourceIP", "destinationIP") AS 'Source or Destination IP',
       QIDNAME(qid) AS 'Event Name',
       Category AS 'Low Level Category',
       "sourceIP" AS 'Source IP',
       "destinationIP" AS 'Destination IP',
       LOGSOURCENAME(logsourceid) AS 'Log Source Name',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(devicetime, 'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'First Seen',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(starttime, 'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'Start Time',
       "userName" AS 'Username',
       SUM("eventCount") AS 'Event Count (Sum)',
       COUNT(*) AS 'Count'
FROM events
WHERE INOFFENSE(#id#)
  AND logSourceId NOT IN (113, 63)
GROUP BY SET("sourceIP", "destinationIP")
ORDER BY "Count"
LAST 24 HOURS
```

