# URL / DNS / Malware Queries

## URL Events

**Context:**  
Analyse des événements contenant des URLs (firewall, proxy).

```aql
SELECT "Hostname" AS 'Device',
       "URL" AS 'Link',
       "Service Name" AS 'Method',
       "Action" AS 'Firewall Decision',
       QIDNAME(qid) AS 'Event Name',
       LOGSOURCENAME(logsourceid) AS 'Log Source Name',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(devicetime,'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'First Seen',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(starttime,'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'Start Time'
FROM events
WHERE INOFFENSE(#id#)
  AND logSourceId NOT IN (113, 63)
  AND "URL" IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY "Hostname","URL","Service Name","Action",qid,logsourceid
ORDER BY "Hostname"
LAST 7 HOURS
```

***

## DNS Analysis

**Context:**  
DNS hostnames suspects associés à une offense.

```aql
SELECT "URL Host" AS 'URL Host',
       "DNS Request Type" AS 'Request Type',
       "Error Code" AS 'DNS Code',
       "Subtype" AS 'DNS Actions',
       QIDNAME(qid) AS 'Event Name',
       LOGSOURCENAME(logsourceid) AS 'Log Source Name',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(devicetime,'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'First Seen',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(starttime,'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'Start Time'
FROM events
WHERE INOFFENSE(#id#)
  AND logSourceId NOT IN (113, 63)
  AND "URL Host" IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY "URL Host", "DNS Request Type", "Error Code", "Subtype", qid, logsourceid
ORDER BY "URL Host"
LAST 7 HOURS
```

