## Malware Summary

**Context:**  
Résumé global (IP, catégories, comptes) d’une activité malware.

```aql
SELECT SET("sourceIP", "destinationIP") AS 'Source or Destination IP',
       UniqueCount(qid) AS 'Event Name (Unique Count)',
       UniqueCount(category) AS 'Low Level Category (Unique Count)',
       UniqueCount(logSourceId) AS 'Log Source (Unique Count)',
       UniqueCount("sourceIP") AS 'Source IP (Unique Count)',
       UniqueCount("destinationIP") AS 'Destination IP (Unique Count)',
       UniqueCount("userName") AS 'Username (Unique Count)',
       SUM("eventCount") AS 'Event Count (Sum)',
       COUNT(*) AS 'Count'
FROM events
WHERE INOFFENSE(#id#)
  AND logSourceId NOT IN (113, 63)
GROUP BY SET("sourceIP", "destinationIP")
ORDER BY "Count"
LAST 24 HOURS
```

